    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/091e921aed10d0a0c21efb372b092e0b.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/091e921aed10d0a0c21efb372b092e0b.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经营一间属于自己的寿司店吧</h2>在一个奇幻的地下世界中管理你的寿司食堂，并以奇特的料理来满足客人的味蕾。升级你的餐厅让客人变得越来越多吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/f6f3f41d531b6f5f58a55eb52cc8da03.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/f6f3f41d531b6f5f58a55eb52cc8da03.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >把可爱的怪物们做成美味的料理！</h2>洞穴中居住着许多独特又迷人的生物。从他们身上收集珍贵的食材，以解锁各种食谱来满足顾客的需求。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/fce3e78b336524ff5a2167bc7563a2ce.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/fce3e78b336524ff5a2167bc7563a2ce.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精心打造的2.5D手绘地窖</h2>辛苦工作之馀，停下脚步欣赏这美丽的世界吧！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/7cf99851f071939c9223120fe861bf5d.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/7cf99851f071939c9223120fe861bf5d.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >传说中的茶碗蒸</h2>没有茶碗蒸的世界是黯淡无光的！为了完美重现这道神秘料理，从食材的收集到厨艺的磨练缺一不可，你 ... 准备好了吗？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/d539bd15e9d163d6ea5795345084ce19.poster.avif?t=1730712894\" width=620 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050530/extras/d539bd15e9d163d6ea5795345084ce19.webm?t=1730712894\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
